createMine 
Game: Armed Assault (1.00) 
Description: Creates a mine of the given type (type is the name of the subclass 
 of CfgVehicles). If the markers array contains several marker names 
, the position of a random one is used, otherwise, the given position 
 is used. The mine is placed inside a circle with this position as its center 
 and placement as its radius.  
Syntax:  
 Object = createMine [type, position, markers, placement] 
Parameters: 
[type, position, markers, placement]: Array 
type: String 
position: Position 
markers: Array 
placement: Number radius 
Return Value: 
 Object